{"tid":2055523,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對住同路人，與其屌人老母，不如試着說「不完美可改善」","createTime":"2020-06-08T04:38:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-08T04:57:53.000Z","uid":3560,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"38c6264a4ab8879a2d3a4d2ded6f73292111da9a","tid":2055523,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T04:38:35.000Z","msg":"黃店好多嘢都抵屌<br />\n難食抵屌，抽水抵屌<br />\n當大家擁有批判思考，更多嘢會想屌或者覺得對方可以做好啲<br />\n但與其下下都大大力屌人老母然後無限發酵<br />\n不如試着說一句「不完美可接受可改善」就算<br />\n對住同路人，說話可以留一線<br />\n做大個餅最重要<br />\n<br />\n對住藍店/確定嘅僞黃先大大力屌啦<br />\n<br />\n說好的團結不割席呢。"},{"pid":"ee746085fdb757976756149cf08a49de7b2ef508","tid":2055523,"uid":53675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T04:41:52.000Z","msg":"推 認同"},{"pid":"0a52fd11d0338fe7dab155a24275ccc46a0108f9","tid":2055523,"uid":60881,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T04:42:03.000Z","msg":"agree"},{"pid":"d91544a0d9b1dad94817f9df0feed4d76b2e2a38","tid":2055523,"uid":158996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T04:43:45.000Z","msg":"Be humble 全部都笑話嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab3454884fb8d75bbd33a199e85d6c442fcfd97a","tid":2055523,"uid":65091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d91544a0d9b1dad94817f9df0feed4d76b2e2a38","tid":2055523,"uid":158996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T04:43:45.000Z","msg":"Be humble 全部都笑話嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T04:47:28.000Z","msg":"be humble咁屌人老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3e0360bfd1ee0070c34f9e3d72fef8c9e5f8d62","tid":2055523,"uid":35814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T04:49:11.000Z","msg":"主要係討論方面<br />\n莫講話老母<br />\n其實唔應該講野難聽<br />\n以理服人<br />\n呢四個字好易明，但好難做<br />\n已經唔係叫你面對面即時回覆<br />\n出文鬧人或串人之前諗下有冇必要咁做<br />\n最重要係鬧人同串人好多時嘅結果只係自己爽<br />\